  "description": [
    "III kuliiiu The policy of this store is to keep the prices of the goods in stock on the level with the prices of the goods in the wholesale market There have been many articles given nation wide circulation with regard to prices but the only reductions that have come so far have been as a result of the drops in prices of the raw materials Many customers feel that the same drop should be made in the finished product for example let us take womens wear Roughly speaking the prices are from 15 to 20 per cent lower than they were at the peak last February There are two distinct elements which control the price of such goodsLABOR and MATERIAL Silk stuffs are from 40 to 50 per cent below the peak Woolens do not average more than 20 per cent less than the peak prices THERE HAS BEEN ABSOLUTELY NO REDUCTION IN prices THE COST OF LABOR i A V f OUR RECONSTRUCTION PERIOD SALE IS A CONSCIENTIOUS EFFORT TO REDUCE PRICES AND ESTABLISH A NEW PURCHASING VALUE FOR YOU RDOLLAR SALE STARTS FRIDAY NOV 12th X DRESS GOODS REDUCED LADIES SILK UNDERWEAR Discounted LADIESSUITS LADIES COATS from"
  ],
